3.00	Nikolai_Yakovlevich_Marr	Nicholas Marr	Nicholas Jakovlevich Marr was a Georgia-born historian and linguist who gained a reputation as a scholar of the Caucasus during the 1910s before developing his linguistic "Japhetic theory" on the origin of language (from 1924) and related speculative linguistic hypotheses.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7a/Marr.jpg
